  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/4zB141x-xHc?si=2SPfcJ0D9aVZsrz-\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br>\nTo activate your Enterprise Search product, Administrators should navigate to the Product Activation tab on the left sidebar navigation in <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0041be; text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;\" target=\"_blank\">Customer Portal</a> and select </span><strong>Enterprise Search.</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On this page, you will be able to download </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">licenses for each subscription term</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"enterprise_search.PNG\" src=\"https://support.liferay.com/documents/d/customer-portal/8867974562445-enterprise_search\" style=\"border: #E9EBF0 1px solid;\"></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Enterprise Search activation is typically available for subscriptions with a start date in the current quarter or previous quarters. If your subscription start date falls in a future quarter, </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">you will receive an error stating that your key is not yet available. Please return to this page at a later time. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have any questions about the availability of your Enterprise Search activation key, please contact our Liferay Support Team for further assistance by opening a </span><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com\">support ticket</a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>"
      },
